" ijkl instead of hjkl {{{
nnoremap j h
vnoremap j h
nnoremap i k
vnoremap i k
nnoremap k j
vnoremap k j

" since 'i' is now used for motion, make 'h' do what 'i' used to
nnoremap h i
nnoremap H I
vnoremap h i
vnoremap H I
nnoremap I H

" operator pending mode. biggest impact is all the 'inner' mappings use h instead of i
" onoremap j h
" onoremap i k
" onoremap k j
